column2:
@w2 <color=#00ffcc><b>Hun, maybe you could help us out with a little problem.</b></color>
@w2 <color=#00ffcc><b>As you no doubt noticed, the situation here isn't good.</b><b></b></color>
@w2 <color=#00ffcc><b>I'm sure like the rest of us here, you're interested in remaining alive? </b></color>
@w2 <color=#00ffcc><b>You seem the capable type.</b></color><color=#00ffcc><b></b></color>

@w1 <color=#ffffff>Bugtron Weapons Systems</color>
@w1 <color=#d1e916><b>Bugtron 1</b> - </color><color=#00fa2a>Enemy Targeting Systems </color><b><color=#fa0000>Active</color></b>
@w1 <color=#d1e916><b>Bugtron 2</b></color><color=#d1e916> - </color><color=#00fa2a>Enemy Targeting</color><color=#00fa2a> Systems </color><b><color=#fa0000>Active</color></b>
@w1 <color=#d1e916><b>Bugtron 3</b> </color><color=#d1e916></color><color=#d1e916>- </color><color=#00fa2a>Enemy Targeting</color><color=#00fa2a> Systems </color><b><color=#fa0000>Active</color></b>

@w3<color=#d1e916> *3DXzJG3</color><color=#fa0000>TURRETS</color><color=#d1e916>09dfnFv0Xnk</color><color=#fa0000>ACTIVATED</color><color=#d1e916>^GH3h8GS872HK2</color>
@w3 <color=#d1e916>1</color><color=#fa0000>0</color><color=#d1e916>00ENGAGE11  01 </color><color=#fa0000>001 0</color><color=#d1e916> 11111 0 0</color><color=#fa0000>0</color><color=#d1e916>  0THREAT LEVEL1 </color><color=#fa0000>000 1 1 </color><color=#d1e916>1 10 </color><color=#fa0000>RED </color><color=#d1e916>1</color>
@w1 <color=#fa0000>{PlayerName} </color><color=#d1e916>TARGET ACQUIRED</color><color=#fa0000>. </color>
@w1 <color=#fa0000><i>ALL PERSONNEL, READY THREAT LEVEL RED</i></color><color=#fa0000></color>
@w1 <color=#fa0000><i>ALL PERSONNEL, TAKE IMMEDIATE SECURITY MEASURES</i></color><color=#fa0000></color>

@w1 <color=#00ffcc><b>Alright, good luck. Be careful in there, it's gnarly.</b></color>
@w1 <color=#00ffcc><b>I'll call you once the radio is online. </b></color>
@w1 <color=#00ffcc><b>Here, take these, probably come in handy. </b></color>
@w1 <color=#ffffff>(She reaches under the bar and collects a small pile of medikits for you)</color><color=#00ffcc><b></b></color>

@w2 <color=#00ffcc><b>I thought so. Got a keen eye. </b></color>
@w2 <color=#00ffcc><b>While we'd all love to keep this party going until our livers give out, prudence dictates we try to get the hell outta here, ideally with our heads still attached to our bodies.</b></color><color=#00ffcc><b></b></color>
@w2 <color=#00ffcc><b>Problem is, see that main exit over there.</b> </color><color=#ffffff>(she points behind you)</color><color=#00ffcc></color>
@w2 <b><color=#00ffcc>Yeah, it's offline. There's an emergency exit of course, galactic fire code and all.</color></b>

@w1 <color=#04ecdd>Good...</color>
@w2 <color=#c2c2c2>(the lab worker is visibly shaking now)</color>
@w1 <color=#04ecdd>Raptors.</color><color=#c2c2c2></color>
@w1 <color=#04ecdd>You need to get in there and shut down the replicators.</color><color=#ffffff></color>

@w1 <color=#04ecdd>Here</color>
@w2 <color=#c2c2c2>(the lab worker tosses you a PDA)</color>
@w1 <color=#04ecdd>I can walk you through it once you get in there.</color>
@w1 <color=#04ecdd>Take out any raptors in your way. I hope you brought enough ammo.</color>

@w3 <color=#ff0000>Spamming the system... </color>
@w4 <color=#ff0000>Er2YCfh   JqZjs5eaPupnKc   x6zBg9RA87DLmX3HTvd   7hQM   yVk   bwG... </color>
@w2 <color=#ff0000>[The spam software completes without errors] </color>
@w2 <color=#ffffff>rebooting...</color><color=#ff0000></color>

@w3 <color=#07e421>Overclocking the system... </color>
@w4 <color=#07e421>Hr2Y8fh   1qZjs5eaHupnK5   p6zBg9RA87DLmX3HTv9   4UQx   y9k   3w4... </color>
@w2 <color=#07e421>[The overclock software completes without errors] </color>
@w2 <color=#ffffff>rebooting...</color><color=#07e421></color>

@w3 <color=#007bff>Fortifying the system... </color>
@w4 <color=#007bff>vr2Ywfh   5qZjsrFaHu4io7   4hjKg9RA99xLmX4hTv9   9gJ7   33g   6h2... </color>
@w2 <color=#007bff>[The fortify software completes without errors] </color>
@w2 <color=#ffffff>rebooting...</color><color=#007bff></color>

@w2 Smart choice. Here.
@w2 <color=#ffffff>(He tosses you a PDA) </color>
@w2 I'll ping you on comms if I need you. 
@w2 Head to the Abandoned Pyramid. Take out any Smugglers you encounter.
